🧘‍♀️ I've teamed up with @VodafoneUK to help make the nation more flexible this summer with VodaYoga (which I helped create!), a yoga flow designed in partnership with @Nuffield.Health. We wanted to combat the effects of too much sitting down and being sedentary 🦥 It also includes some of my favourite go-to moves for maintaining and improving my flexibility in training 💪

VodaYoga marks the launch of Vodafone EVO, a new ‘flexible’ mobile offering (see what we did there?!) giving customers ultimate flexibility on contract lengths, flexibility on trading-in their old smartphone and flexible upgrades. 

New research shows that on average we are sitting down for more than 43 hours each week and a quarter of you are suffering from more aches and strains than ever before. 

So grab your mat, water bottle, and get flexible!! Full routine available to view in my bio! #ad
